This version of Terminaux is a late monthly release that adds some new features.

This release is now available as a celebratory event of our Aptivi Blog being selected for the Sunshine Blogger Award for the second time!

### Changes

This release contains a variety of changes, including, but not limited to:

- `[+]` Added accurate progress bar design
- `[+]` Added pane-specific keybindings
- `[+]` Added link markup
- `[*]` Fixed ImageMagick security bugs
- `[*]` General improvements and bug fixes

Review the commit history if you want to get a deep insight about the changes.

### Feedback?

If you have issues with this version, report to us by [making a new issue ticket](https://github.com/Aptivi/Terminaux/issues/new).

